Critical Authority.descriptor: Essential critical voices from major institutions known for depth, rigorous standards, and long-standing industry trust.

Tastemakers.descriptor: Digital trendsetters and established indie mainstays driving the current musical conversation.

Specialists.descriptor: Niche expert curators focused on deep cuts, avant-garde discoveries, and specific genre depth.

Mainstream.descriptor: High-frequency media outlets and lifestyle sources tracking mass cultural appeal and global broadcasting trends.
